# CSharp Console Task Manager

A simple console-based task manager written in CSharp.

This project was created to practise core software development concepts in preparation for a Software Development Level 4 apprenticeship application.

## Features
- Add tasks
- View tasks
- Exit the application cleanly

## Concepts Demonstrated
- Object-oriented programming (classes and objects)
- Lists and basic data structures
- Control flow (loops and conditionals)
- Console input and output

## Notes
This project focuses on clarity and structure rather than advanced features or persistence.
